      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by a doctor last week but the cut is looking kinda weird today. it's pretty red and feels warm to the touch and there's some yellow stuff oozing out a little bit. is that normal or should i be worried? can i just put a warm compress on it and some neosporin to fix it up?",
