      "content": "wait so the neosporin is bad? i thought that was what you were supposed to use for cuts. if i just do the warm compress and the regular ointment and keep it bandaged up, it should clear up on its own in a couple days right? i really dont want to go back to the clinic and pay for another appointment if i can just handle it here.",
